dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Shows northeastern England. Includes illustrations of a ship and a sea monster in ocean. Does not match any states listed in Van der Krogt. From the Appendix Atlas of the British Isles and Northern Europe, title created to represent a unique collection within the Clark Library, University of Michigan. 1 map: 54x 44 cm.
